-- RWE Workers in Germany Plan to Strike Thursday and Friday in Pay Dispute
-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 2010-12-15T09:16:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/rwe-workers-in-germany-plan-to-strike-thursday-and-friday-in-pay-dispute.html
RWE AG employees in Germany will
hold strikes on Thursday and Friday in a pay dispute with the
Essen-based utility, Michael Winkler, a worker representative
with the IG BCE labor union, said today by phone.  He declined to provide additional information on the
planned walkouts before 12 midday local time today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
